X = \left(U + V\right)/2\,,\quad Y = \left(U - V\right)/2
F\left(u,v\right)=P\left\{ U\leq u\wedge V\leq v\right\} =P\left\{ X+Y\leq u\wedge X-Y\leq v\right\} =\iint_{A}dxdy
A=\left\{ \left(x,y\right)\in\left[0,1\right]^{2}\mid x+y\leq u\wedge x-y\leq v\right\} 
f\left(u,v\right)=\left(d^{2}/dudv\right)F\left(u,v\right)
